{"tid":1197543,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"王丹: 林鄭堅持惡法, 說明中共出現了管治危機","createTime":"2019-06-10T04:11:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T07:32:24.000Z","uid":134071,"like":56,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"6899cecbad3e3254c51f0d9992e11efb354e810f","tid":1197543,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T04:11:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/permalink.php?story_fbid=10156335976608027&amp;id=105759983026&amp;comment_tracking=%7B%22tn%22%3A%22O%22%7D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpermalink.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D10156335976608027%26id%3D105759983026%26comment_tracking%3D%257B%2522tn%2522%253A%2522O%2522%257D&d=QYvF2KwMlxx6JcZ5CCC9GLQTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=1ec85ba1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/permalink.php?story_fbid=10156335976608027&amp;id=105759983026&amp;comment_tracking=%7B%22tn%22%3A%22O%22%7D</a><br />\n<br />\n王丹網站 Wang Dan's Page<br />\n2 小時 &middot;<br />\n<br />\n香港昨天百萬人上街反對惡法，全球響應，西方各國也表達關切。在這樣的情況下，中共仍下令港府堅持修法，完全不顧民意。這說明了什麼？<br />\n<br />\n這說明中共出現了管治危機。<br />\n<br />\n當年要推二十三條，50萬人上街，<strong>江澤民下令推遲立法，隔年董建華下台。香港形勢暫時穩住，中共空間換時間，得以慢慢分化滲透，才有今天對香港的全面控制。</strong><br />\n<br />\n習近平的水平低，就表現在他除了一意孤行之外，沒有任何其他的現代治理的手段。這樣的結果，最終是激起人民的反彈<strong>。百萬人的憤怒，是會讓中共付出代價的。</strong>這個道理，習近平不懂。<br />\n<br />\n他這麼傻，真好。"},{"pid":"436f9a2a776171b2a71f585522a16712a54c9db9","tid":1197543,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T04:11:35.000Z","msg":"出錯版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae95f5bd1bba1d569be3fdd4610f741cb478ba9c","tid":1197543,"uid":106326,"like":23,"dislike":6,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T04:12:55.000Z","msg":"王丹這麼傻，真好。"},{"pid":"b0892f4adfcc97b4bc5d819d6cb43318be94c0a4","tid":1197543,"uid":134071,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"ae95f5bd1bba1d569be3fdd4610f741cb478ba9c","tid":1197543,"uid":106326,"like":23,"dislik